node.text: We partnered with #GoodToVote! If we can get 500 of you to register to vote—or simply check your registration—we will host the first-ever Laguna Beach cast Reunion! It takes minutes to register, and even less to check! Even if you think you’re already registered, please check to make sure! Link in Bio

node.text: @TheLittleMarket x @SajeWellness collaboration is finally here! My co-founder, @HannahSkvarla, and I teamed up with Saje to design the limited-edition Aroma Mosaic diffuser. To celebrate this collaboration, Saje made a generous donation to support The Little Market’s mission to empower women in breaking the cycle of poverty. The diffuser is available now at Saje stores and on Saje.com.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Lauren Conrad on May 05, 2021 tagging @thelittlemarket, and @laurenconradbeauty. May be an image of cosmetics.

node.text:
To celebrate motherhood, we put together a giveaway from two of my brands @thelittlemarket and @LaurenConradBeauty. One winner will receive 2 sets of prizes, one for themselves and 1 for a mom figure in their life. 

The winner will get 2 sets of $250 gift cards from The Little Market and Lauren Conrad Beauty. Total prize valued at $1,000. 

Here’s how to enter: 
1. Follow @TheLittleMarket and LaurenConradBeauty
2. Like this post!
3. Comment below and tag friends who would want to enter.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⁣
Giveaway ends Sunday, May 9th, at 11:59PM PT. One winner will be chosen at random. Winners will be announced on Monday, May 10th. Must be a U.S. resident, 18 years or older to enter.

node.text: Wishing everyone a happy and healthy Easter 🐰

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Lauren Conrad on March 31, 2021 tagging @katemartindalestylist, and @thelittlemarket. May be an image of flower.

node.text: Today is the last day of Women’s History Month! If you haven’t had a chance to listen to the Conversations with Changemakers series yet then I encourage you to go to TheLittleMarket.com and check them out. We were so lucky to have some amazing individuals participate in honest conversations about issues that impact women globally. Link in bio 🤍

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Lauren Conrad on March 08, 2021 tagging @hannahskvarla, and @thelittlemarket. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and outdoors.

node.text: Last year we celebrated International Women’s Day by gathering with a group of amazing women who have all supported @thelittlemarket. It was a special day, not only because of what we were celebrating, but because it was the last time I spoke with and hugged so many people I love. This year we’re celebrating a little differently. @thelittlemarket will be hosting an online series called Conversations with Changemakers. Each day we will be releasing a new conversation about an issue that impacts women globally. Our first conversation is available at thelittlemarket.com today. Link in bio. #conversationswithchangemakers

node.text:
On March 8th, International Women’s Day, @thelittlemarket will be launching our virtual series Conversation with Changemakers.
We invite you to join us as we bring together activists, celebrities, and thought leaders to talk, learn, and inspire us all through a series of thought-provoking conversations available online to everyone, everywhere. I’m so proud of our team for making this happen and I can’t wait for everyone to listen to these incredible conversations. For more information please visit thelittlemarket.com
